               <scopecontent id="aspace_3c3c2e2db6724db19792bfb6795d2754">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Includes bookplates of the following individuals: James H. Blauvelt, Elihu Chauncey, Herbert Duncan Crouch, Elizabeth Downe, Hilda B. Edwards, H. S. Ehrismann, Virginia C. Fraley, Leo. M. Franklin, Herbert John Gladstone, Richard E. Glass, Betty J. Leary, George J. Molnar, M.D., John Monks, Thomas B. Mosher, Calvin Neff, Angelica Van Vranken Olmstead, Elizabeth A. Otis, Dewey Pils, J. W. F. Podmore, Alfred Robinson, Howard C. Smith, W. S. Summers, Welles, Pliny Jewell Wilson, E. H. Worcester, John and Nancy Worcester, and Unidentified [Don Quixote design].</p>
                  <p>Includes bookplates of the following institutions: Adelbert College-Western Reserve University, Brooklyn College Library, de Grey &amp; Ripon, Loomis Institute Library, San Diego College for Women, Sondley Reference Library, Trinity Parish Library-Southport, CT, Yale Medical Library, and Young Women's Christian Association-National Training School.</p>
               </scopecontent>
